== Quellen

+ Wouthuyzen-Bakker M, et al. Guideline for management of septic arthritis in native joints (SANJO). *J Bone Jt Infect*. 2023;8:29–37. https://pmc.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/articles/PMC9901514/ (Abruf: 2026-07-14).
